body:
Leading up to a knee replacement operation my husband experienced a severe reaction to an antibiotic. The swift action and superb communication of;
the pre assessment team at The Alex (NHS), Cheadle Hulme Health centre and 
the Chemist in Cheadle Hulme (staff and Pharmacist), meant that a quick change of antibiotic was possible with both the GP and Consultant’s approval and for the operation to go ahead on schedule (today). Thank you all for your perseverance and kindness.
